Description: Extends 'blockr.core' with interactive blocks for data
    visualization using Apache ECharts via 'echarts4r'. Includes universal
    chart blocks (scatter, line, bar, area, pie), specialized blocks
    (heatmap, radar, sankey, gauge, candlestick, calendar, treemap),
    and a hierarchical filter block (sunburst, treemap, tree).
